sectionText: ALL ACCY 202 SECTIONS RESTRICTED TO COLLEGE OF BUSINESS, ACE, ACES, CS & GE MAJORS.  ALL OTHERS MAY ENROLL AT 10 AM ON NOV. 21 IF SPACE IS AVAILABLE. Accountancy course prerequisites are strictly enforced.  The Accounting Department will not allow students to advance in the accounting curriculum if they have not met the required prerequisite for previous accountancy courses taken.
